    {
      "id": "6a09afcfb1d9387f6511a71e",
      "text": "明晰主義",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779019730,
      "updated": 1779019730
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09afba0000000000018ec9",
      "text": " 文章の本質的価値は「明晰さ」にあるとする立場[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779019730,
      "updated": 1779019763
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09afd70000000000018ecb",
      "text": "  [森鴎外]の「一に明晰、二に明晰、三に明晰」はそれをよく表している",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779019759,
      "updated": 1779019831
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b01e0000000000018ecd",
      "text": "  [谷崎潤一郎]や[三島由紀夫]の文章読本でもこのような考え方が語られている",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779019831,
      "updated": 1779020919
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b0190000000000018ecc",
      "text": "  「明晰主義」は私の仮用語",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779019826,
      "updated": 1779020035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b0f00000000000018ed0",
      "text": "   「美文晰文」とも",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1779020040,
      "updated": 1779020061
    },
    {
      "id": "6a09b0e30000000000018ecf",
